PURPOSE OF THIS REPOSITORY
================================================================================

This repository holds canonical reference files for AIXYBER TECH LTD. Each
file in this repository serves as the single source of truth for its subject
area and is referenced from other AIXYBER and Q-SAG substrate repositories.

Files in this repository:

  README.md                  — overview of the repository
  company-facts.md           — corporate identity, registered details
  pgp-key.txt                — PGP public key for security communications
  security.txt               — RFC 9116 coordinated disclosure pointer
  coordinated-disclosure.md  — full coordinated disclosure policy
  AI_ASSISTANCE.md           — AI assistance disclosure policy
  governance.md              — current governance model
  substrate-programme.md     — Q-SAG substrate programme overview
  secure-by-design.md        — CISA Secure by Design pledge status

